### Get Inquiries (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8088/api/contact?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get Inquiry Detail (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8088/api/contact/{{inquiry_id_1}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Respond Inquiry (Admin)
PUT http://localhost:8088/api/contact/{{inquiry_id_1}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "status": "responded",
  "adminResponse": "Hello, fees are 5%."
}

### Get Stats (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8088/api/contact/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
